### **2. BOT POWERS / ACTIONS TO DEPLOY**

- `/ship`: Drop unfinished project, log to #ship-log or DM you a micro-win prompt.
- `/vent`: Private DM to self (or to mod), logs “no-shame” rants.
- `/meme`: AI generates or fetches a meme, injects into chat.
- `/graveyard`: Lists your unfinished “near-lies,” prompts next step.
- `/nobricked`: Trigger escalation (alerts mods, opens support thread).
- `/opslog`: Operator command — logs notable actions, pings channel if sabotage or breakthrough is detected.
- **DM “Wire Closer Protocol”** as a response to “help” or a keyword.

